-- Brazil Credit Card Market Needs More Competition, Central Bank Chief Says
-- Iuri Dantas
-- 2010-06-17T12:24:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/brazil-credit-card-market-needs-more-competition-central-bank-chief-says.html

          
          
             Brazil central bank President
Henrique Meirelles said more competition and transparency is
needed in the credit card market.  
 Meirelles spoke in a video message presented at a seminar
in Rio de Janeiro.  
